Angela walks out and has a meltdown in her room.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:26.320 --> 00:04:30.480
Beth packs her things because she is afraid of the&nbsp;
men that may hurt them if Jackson fails to bring&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:30.480 --> 00:04:34.960
