wakes up in the middle of the night after hearing&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:34.960 --> 00:04:39.920
noises outside her room. She goes downstairs&nbsp;
and sees her mother in the kitchen without eyes.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:40.480 --> 00:04:44.400
She realizes that it is just a nightmare and&nbsp;
talks to her brother about their new client.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:44.960 --> 00:04:49.040
Jackson, needing the money to pay off&nbsp;
the loan sharks, agrees to the job,&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:49.040 --> 00:04:54.640
