to the countryside where the house is located at.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:54.640 --> 00:04:58.320
Angela cannot stop thinking about her dream&nbsp;
and seems bothered during the whole trip.&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:04:58.880 --> 00:05:03.760
They arrive at a gated community, and an old&nbsp;
caretaker opens it for them. All four of them&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:03.760 --> 00:05:09.200
