feeling. Mrs. Greene, the caller, welcomes the&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:09.200 --> 00:05:14.560
team to the home as she gives a tour. Mrs. Greene&nbsp;
is a very traditional woman; she highly values&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:14.560 --> 00:05:19.440
good manners and common etiquette. Jackson hands&nbsp;
her over the payslip, but Mrs. Greene says she&nbsp;&nbsp;

00:05:19.440 --> 00:05:24.480
will sign it after the service is rendered. Angela&nbsp;
begins the interview about Mrs. Greene's concerns.&nbsp;&nbsp;

